## üåê Networking & Downloads

### Network informacije

```bash
# IP adresa i network interfaces
ip addr show                            # Sve network interfaces
ip a                                    # Skraƒáeno
ifconfig                                # Stariji naƒçin (ako je instaliran)
hostname -I                             # Samo IP adrese

# Network connections
netstat -tulpn                          # Svi listening portovi
ss -tulpn                               # Moderniji od netstat
lsof -i :80                             # ≈†ta koristi port 80
sudo netstat -anp | grep :8080          # Proveri port 8080

# DNS i connectivity
ping google.com                         # Proveri konekciju
ping -c 4 google.com                    # Po≈°alji samo 4 paketa
nslookup google.com                     # DNS lookup
dig google.com                          # Detaljni DNS info
host google.com                         # Jednostavan DNS lookup
traceroute google.com                   # Prati rutu do hosta

# Firewall (ufw)
sudo ufw status                         # Status firewall-a
sudo ufw enable                         # Omoguƒái firewall
sudo ufw allow 22                       # Dozvoli port 22 (SSH)
sudo ufw allow 80/tcp                   # Dozvoli port 80 TCP
sudo ufw deny 23                        # Blokiraj port 23
sudo ufw delete allow 80                # Ukloni pravilo
```

### Downloads sa wget i curl

```bash
# Wget - download fajlova
wget https://example.com/file.zip                       # Preuzmi fajl
wget -O custom_name.zip https://example.com/file.zip    # Preuzmi sa custom imenom
wget -c https://example.com/large_file.zip              # Nastavi preuzimanje (-c = continue)
wget -b https://example.com/file.zip                    # Preuzmi u background-u
wget -r https://example.com/directory/                  # Rekurzivno preuzimanje
wget --limit-rate=200k https://example.com/file.zip     # Ograniƒçi brzinu
wget -i urls.txt                                        # Preuzmi sve URL-ove iz fajla

# Curl - transfer podataka
curl https://example.com                                # Prika≈æi sadr≈æaj
curl -O https://example.com/file.zip                    # Preuzmi fajl (ƒçuva original ime)
curl -o custom.zip https://example.com/file.zip         # Preuzmi sa custom imenom
curl -L https://example.com                             # Prati redirects
curl -I https://example.com                             # Samo HTTP headers
curl -s https://api.example.com/data                    # Silent mode (bez progress)

# API requests sa curl
curl -X GET https://api.example.com/users               # GET request
curl -X POST https://api.example.com/users \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"name":"John"}'                                  # POST sa JSON
curl -X DELETE https://api.example.com/users/1          # DELETE request
curl -u username:password https://api.example.com       # Basic auth

# Provera connectivity
curl -I https://google.com                              # Proveri da li je sajt dostupan
curl -o /dev/null -s -w "%{http_code}\n" https://google.com  # Samo HTTP status code
```

### SSH i SCP

```bash
# SSH - remote login
ssh username@hostname                                   # Osnovna konekcija
ssh username@192.168.1.100                              # Konekcija sa IP
ssh -p 2222 username@hostname                           # Custom port
ssh -i ~/.ssh/id_rsa username@hostname                  # Sa specific key
ssh -L 8080:localhost:80 username@hostname              # Port forwarding

# SCP - secure copy
scp file.txt username@hostname:/path/to/destination     # Kopiraj na remote
scp username@hostname:/path/to/file.txt .               # Kopiraj sa remote
scp -r directory/ username@hostname:/path/              # Kopiraj direktorijum
scp -P 2222 file.txt username@hostname:/path/           # Custom SSH port

# Rsync - sinhronizacija (efikasnija od scp)
rsync -avz source/ username@hostname:/destination/      # Sync sa remote
rsync -avz username@hostname:/source/ ./destination/    # Sync sa remote
# a - archive mode, v - verbose, z - kompresija
```

