## üîß Package Management (apt)

```bash
# A≈æuriranje sistema
sudo apt update                         # A≈æuriraj listu paketa
sudo apt upgrade                        # Instaliraj a≈æuriranja
sudo apt full-upgrade                   # Upgrade sa dependencies handling
sudo apt dist-upgrade                   # Distribution upgrade

# Instalacija i brisanje
sudo apt install package_name           # Instaliraj paket
sudo apt install package1 package2      # Instaliraj vi≈°e paketa
sudo apt remove package_name            # Ukloni paket
sudo apt purge package_name             # Ukloni paket i config fajlove
sudo apt autoremove                     # Ukloni nepotrebne dependencies

# Pretraga i informacije
apt search keyword                      # Pretra≈æi pakete
apt show package_name                   # Detalji o paketu
apt list --installed                    # Lista instaliranih paketa
apt list --upgradable                   # Lista paketa za upgrade

# ƒåi≈°ƒáenje
sudo apt clean                          # Obri≈°i preuzete .deb fajlove
sudo apt autoclean                      # Obri≈°i stare verzije
```

